decogo.solver.results¶

Stores the results obtained by the solver

Classes

Results()

Class which stores and makes some manipulations with the results.
class decogo.solver.results.Results[source]¶

Class which stores and makes some manipulations with the results. The results are: primal/dual bound, primal solution point, timings, gap
